==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interpenetration
<hw>In`ter*pen`e*tra"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act
or process of penetrating between or within other substances; mutual
penetration; also, the result of a process of interpenetration.</def>
<rj><au>Milman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interpenetrative</ent>⟦br⟧
